Package com.webobjects.woextensions Description

The WebObjects Extensions are non-synchronizing reusable components defined in the WebObjects Extensions Framework, which is included in every WebObjects Application project. The source code for this framework is available at /Developer/Examples/WebObjects/Source/WOExtensions.

Reference documentation for the Extensions is in the document WebObjects Extensions Reference.
